message.body: You know what I just realized? The Saturday we get back is the last day in November! That means I should probably move into the new house next Saturday so I don't have to scramble when we get back. Do you think it's ok I I start moving stuff over there that early?...
Lemme find out when ahmed leaves, theres plenty of room in the attic and porch for things that arent temp sensetive
Cool; at least if I can move my bigger things in saturday that would be great. It would be the 23rd...
